name: Chef Meghna
text: Don‚Äôt forget to wish her and thank her today; I have wished my Tai; and have thanked her not just for being the woman in my life, not just for seeing me through my few ups and mostly downs - but for completing my family over last 10 years.

name: Chef Meghna
text: For last many years, I have cooked for her just like I would have cooked for rest of the family. Like any other family member, she too has tasted my food experiments and her feedback has mattered the most to me then anyone else in my family.

name: Chef Meghna
text:
I urge you to not forget wishing that amazing lady who keeps your home spick and span. The lady whose presence is taken for granted but her absence is so much unfathomable that it can drive you nuts. 

She may not be your immediate family but her presence completes your family.

name: Chef Meghna
text:
100g Maida
80g Butter
80ml Milk 
200gm Condensed milk
1tsp Baking powder
1tsp Baking soda
2 Lemon zests 
1tbs Lemon juice 
For Sugar Glaze :-
2 tbs Lemon juice
